	<description>Integrates the various concepts of procedures that make up a managerial planning and control system from an accounting, performance measurement, behavioural, organisational design, and strategy implementation point of view. The course emphasizes modern performance measurement and control techniques in the context of changing competitive environments.</description>
</course>
<course>
	<id>127</id>
	<title>ADM 4346 Accounting Information Systems Auditing (3 units)</title>
