</course>
<course>
	<id>128</id>
	<title>ADM 4348 Special Topics in Financial Accounting (3 units)</title>
	<description>Covers specialized topics in financial reporting, including accounting for not-for-profit organizations, leases, benefit plans, and corporate income taxes.</description>
</course>
<course>
	<id>129</id>
	<title>ADM 4349 Advanced Accounting (3 units)</title>
